user.biography: The “Thrill Capital of the World,” theme park boasts world-class roller coasters and 100 rides, games and attractions for the entire family.

node.text: Throw your hands up and high-five if you dare!

node.title: National High Five Day at the Thrill Capital of the World!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on August 07, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Can you name this ride? They prefer to work in the shadows...👀

#ThrillCapitaloftheWorld #SixFlagsMagicMountain #TheThrillisCalling #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on August 06, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Name a better way of enjoying this California weather? 😎🌞
#ThrillCapitaloftheWorld #SupermanEscapefromKrypton #SixflagsMagicMountain #TheThrillisCalling #LosAngeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on August 05, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
4,370 feet of contorted green steel, that lead to a total of 6 inversions. Are you ready?
#thrillcapitaloftheworld #sixflagsmagicmountain #thethrilliscalling #theriddlersrevenge #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on August 02, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text: #MondayMood: Ninja has us hanging on tight to get through the week! 🤪🎢 #sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #thethrilliscalling #ninja #rollercoaster #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 31, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Do you know the original track color of Gold Rusher? Hint: It's not gold 🙃🎢 
#sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #thethrilliscalling #goldrusher #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 29, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text: Coiling track, corkscrews and zig zags. Name a better coaster trio. You can't! 😎🎢🐍 #sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #thethrilliscalling #viper #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 28, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
360-degree rotating seats, face down drops, 200-feet in the air, and fifth-dimensional dives, twists, and flips. Need we say more? 🙌🎢😲
#sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #X2 #thethrilliscalling #rollercoaster #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 17, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Six SixFlags HIIII MAGIC MOUNTAIN H SixFlags LOS ANGELES Park Update Effective 11:59 PM Saturday, July 17, masks will be required at all indoor locations at Six Flags Magic Mountain and Hurricane Harbor, regardless of vaccination status. It is still highly recommended that unvaccinated guests always wear a mask while in the park. We thank you for helping to keep Six Flags safe.'.

node.text: For more info on our park updates, visit https://sixflags.com/magicmountain

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 15, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
If you had to choose the best coaster to sit front row, what would it be and why is it Goliath? 🙃🎢
#sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #thethrilliscalling #goliath #rollercoaster #losangeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 02, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Feel the independence on the world's first 360-degree looping coaster during @CocaCola's July 4th Fest today July 2-July 4! 🇺🇸🎆🎢 Plus don't miss our spectacular fireworks and laser show at 9:15pm each evening! 
#Revolution #SixFlagsMagicMountain #ThrillCapitaloftheWorld #TheThrillisCalling #July4 #CocaCola #FireworksShow #Fireworks #LosAngeles

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Six Flags Magic Mountain on July 01, 2021. May be an image of fireworks.

node.text:
@cocacola’s July 4th Fest is back tomorrow thru Sunday, July 2-4! 🇺🇸🎆🎢 Enjoy your favorite thrilling coasters, a dazzling fireworks and laser show each night, and more! 
#July4 #SixFlagsMagicMountain #ThrillCapitaloftheWorld #TheThrillisCalling #LosAngeles

node.text:
In celebration of 50 years of the steepEST coasters on the planet…Can you name this former coaster first introduced in 1992 as the world's only hairpin drop roller coaster? 🎢🙌
#flashbackfriday #FBF #sixflagsmagicmountain #thrillcapitaloftheworld #thethrilliscalling #50thanniversary
